703903f-a.text:
Cropsey Ave., south side, on line of Bay 26th Street, showing the Hotel Bensonhurst, no longer in existence. In 1890, the Bath Beach Hotel, was on this site, and later it was enlarged and given the name of Hotel
Bensonhurst.
About 1900.
Eugene L. Armbruster Collection.
